                        </div>
                        <div id="question4" class="panel-collapse collapse" style="height: 0px;">
                            <div class="panel-body">
                                <h5><span class="label label-primary">Answer</span></h5>

                                <p>Well, lucky for you. We are not charging any of you in the current stage. Since the system might still consist of several unknown bugs or errors which could not be considered as a final deployment solution. We would like to provide our service to our customers, and that is you. In return, we would like your feedback on our system and report any notable bugs or experiences as much as possible. <span class="text-muted">Yeah...I am still waiting for that $500 from that bastard. </span>Of course, we will let you know if we cannot pay for what we bet some day.</p>
